<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>View Review</title>
    <link href="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.5.2/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        
        .review-container {
            margin: 20px;
        }
        .review-box {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .star-rating {
            color: #ffc107;
        }
        
        .delete-button:hover {
            background-color: red;
            color: white;
        }
       
        .send-button:hover {
            background-color: #333;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <nav aria-label="breadcrumb">
        <ol class="breadcrumb">
            <li class="breadcrumb-item"><a href="#">Admin</a></li>
            <li class="breadcrumb-item"><a href="#">Review</a></li>
            <li class="breadcrumb-item active" aria-current="page">View Review</li>
        </ol>
    </nav>
    
    <div class="container review-container">
        <br><br>
        <div class="review-box">
            <p>Midhun</p>
            <br>
            <p>User-friendly and well-organized. The ability to preview books before buying is a fantastic feature. Looking forward to more updates and discounts!</p>
            <div class="star-rating">
                <span>&#9733;</span>
                <span>&#9733;</span>
                <span>&#9733;</span>
                <span>&#9733;</span>
                <span>&#9734;</span>
            </div>
            <br>
        
        <form>
            <div class="form-group">
                <label for="date">Date</label>
                <input type="date" class="form-control" id="date" value="2024-12-10">
            </div>
            <br>
            <div class="form-group">
                <label for="reply">Reply</label>
                <textarea class="form-control" id="reply" rows="4"></textarea>
            </div>
            <br>
            <button class="btn-danger btn">DELETE</button>
            <button type="submit" class="btn btn-dark">SEND</button>
        </form>
    </div>
    </div>
    <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.5.1.slim.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@popperjs/core@2.5.4/dist/umd/popper.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.5.2/js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
